OL,3,CKeir Starmer to face PMQs for first
OL,4,Ctime since he announced resignation
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer will face Prime
OL,7,FMinister's Questions for the first
OL,8,Ftime since he announced his
OL,9,Fresignation.
OL,11,FThe Prime Minister's Commons outing
OL,12,Fwill mark his first public appearance
OL,13,Fsince the emotional statement he made
OL,14,Fin Downing Street on Monday morning,
OL,15,Fwhen he set out a timetable for his
OL,16,Fexit.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782371887
OL,3,CKeir Starmer to face PMQs for first
OL,4,Ctime since he announced resignation
OL,6,FHe is likely to face questions about
OL,7,Fthe scope of what his Government can
OL,8,Fnow achieve in his final weeks in
OL,9,Foffice, after Downing Street said no
OL,10,F"major" new policy decisions or
OL,11,Fspending pledges would be made before
OL,12,Fa new Labour leader is chosen.
OL,14,FAndy Burnham, Sir Keir's likely
OL,15,Fsuccessor, has been offered Government
OL,16,Fbriefings to prepare for power after
OL,17,FCivil Service access talks were
OL,18,Fauthorised by the Prime Minister.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782371887
OL,3,CKeir Starmer to face PMQs for first
OL,4,Ctime since he announced resignation
OL,6,FThe pair met on Tuesday, the first
OL,7,Ftime since Mr Burnham's Westminster
OL,8,Freturn, in a face-to-face meeting that
OL,9,Ftook place away from No 10 and was
OL,10,Freportedly "frosty", according to the
OL,11,FGuardian.
OL,13,FDespite the promise of no major policy
OL,14,Fdecisions, a row appears to be brewing
OL,15,Fbetween Sir Keir and Mr Burnham over
OL,16,Fthe defence investment plan (Dip), the
OL,17,Fblueprint for future-proofing the
OL,18,Fmilitary that sparked the resignation
OL,19,Fof John Healey as defence secretary
OL,20,Fearlier this month.
OL,26,@rD@LOUrD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
