PN,31504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782371887
OL,3,CKeir Starmer to face PMQs for first
OL,4,Ctime since he announced resignation
OL,6,FSir Keir wants to complete work on the
OL,7,FDip before he leaves Downing Street,
OL,8,Fso he can present it at the Nato
OL,9,Fsummit in Turkey on July 7, as part of
OL,10,Fefforts to establish his legacy as
OL,11,FPrime Minister.
OL,13,FThe plan now provides some #14 billion
OL,14,Fextra funding for the armed forces,
OL,15,Faccording to the Times, though this is
OL,16,Fstill far short of the #28 billion
OL,17,Fmilitary chiefs have called for.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782371887
OL,3,CKeir Starmer to face PMQs for first
OL,4,Ctime since he announced resignation
OL,6,FMr Burnham's camp and allies of Mr
OL,7,FHealey have urged the Prime Minister
OL,8,Fagainst publishing the plan until his
OL,9,Fsuccessor is in place.
OL,11,FTalks are also continuing about who
OL,12,Fmight serve in a Burnham cabinet, and
OL,13,Fwho might advise the former Greater
OL,14,FManchester mayor behind the scenes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
