PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782371887
OL,3,CKeir Starmer to face PMQs for first
OL,4,Ctime since he announced resignation
OL,6,FSenior Labour figures, including
OL,7,Fformer transport secretary Louise
OL,8,FHaigh, Energy Secretary Ed Miliband,
OL,9,FHome Secretary Shabana Mahmood, and
OL,10,Fformer health secretary Wes Streeting,
OL,11,Fhave all been tipped for top jobs in a
OL,12,FGovernment led by Mr Burnham.
OL,14,FJames Purnell, a former Labour cabinet
OL,15,Fminister who served alongside Mr
OL,16,FBurnham in the Blair government, is
OL,17,Fmeanwhile reportedly being sized up as
OL,18,Fa chief of staff, the Times said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
